description:
The multi-talented Shay Mitchell (PRETTY LITTLE LIARS) is here for this week’s all-new episode of Unqualified! First, Anna and Shay talk about working as both actors and producers (7:35) and Shay discusses her experience as part of a predominately female cast on Pretty Little Liars (9:20). Then, Shay answers some deal breakers (12:44) and Anna hosts a round of “How Would You Proceed?” (22:58). Later, they call Lindsay (29:10), who has experienced relationship troubles after revealing her “number”, and Krista (43:00), who is watching a tricky love triangle unfold between her friends. Tune in!

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
